{"tid":731222,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中學嗰陣 有冇遇過老師黑箱作業嘅經歷？","createTime":"2018-07-06T04:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T07:45:27.000Z","uid":137840,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"22168d1d4a5135af81b551e61c00288ec736efda","tid":731222,"uid":137840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:36:13.000Z","msg":"好耐之前 果時讀緊中學<br />\n有年音樂比賽 有個參賽者A同 其中一位評判老師非常熟<br />\n果時我負責計分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後嗰位評判老師俾佢好高分 超出其餘兩三位評判十幾廿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好大出入<br />\n但係佢比其他人嘅分數 好低 徘徊喺50-60 分，但係同學A 80幾分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後果位A同學攞咗冠軍<br />\n依家諗返起都覺得 中學已經黑哨 幾咁可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ef4f026011303bc66f6913dd8b38b8f2810197","tid":731222,"uid":137840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c20b980c5b294caa8c28dbdfbbaa33979c7a75d","tid":731222,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:48:02.000Z","msg":"而家幾大"},{"pid":"0d55d63ef16ba26dcdfdbef855eea825b04bd969","tid":731222,"uid":137840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c20b980c5b294caa8c28dbdfbbaa33979c7a75d","tid":731222,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:48:02.000Z","msg":"而家幾大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:55:57.000Z","msg":"出緊黎做嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 偶爾回味返以前啲日子姐"},{"pid":"7e74a6cc7f110f5e50130f61018d10d3fe043444","tid":731222,"uid":3571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:58:28.000Z","msg":"此回